        "original": "魔法少女ラミィ！",
        "english": "Magical Girl Lamy!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:08.000",
        "end": "00:09.200",
        "original": "ホロウィッチ！",
        "english": "holoWitches!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:09.200",
        "end": "00:11.500",
        "original": "フルキャスト！",
        "english": "Full Cast!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:13.200",
        "end": "00:14.200",
        "original": "行くよ！",
        "english": "Here I go!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:15.200",
        "end": "00:17.000",
        "original": "ほい、ほい、はい！",
        "english": "Hoi, hoi, hai!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:25.700",
        "end": "00:27.500",
        "original": "こん！",
        "english": "Kon!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:32.700",
        "end": "00:34.200",
        "original": "やめな。",
        "english": "Stop it.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:35.000",
        "end": "00:37.000",
        "original": "えい！",
        "english": "Ei!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:00.800",
        "end": "01:02.500",
        "original": "おいおいおい。",
        "english": "Whoa, whoa, whoa.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:21.800",
        "end": "01:25.000",
        "original": "ね、なんかこれ、まずくない？どんどん強くなってる。",
        "english": "Hey, isn't this getting bad? They're getting stronger.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:25.100",
        "end": "01:29.000",
        "original": "みんなが奴らを倒すより、不安と恐れが膨れ上がるほうが早いみたい！",
        "english": "The fear and anxiety are growing faster than you can defeat them!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:29.200",
        "end": "01:31.000",
        "original": "そんな！",
        "english": "No way!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:32.300",
        "end": "01:34.000",
        "original": "うちのせい...",
        "english": "It's my fault...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:38.000",
        "end": "01:42.000",
        "original": "...うちが、あんなもの怖いって思っちゃうせいで...",
        "english": "...because I keep thinking those things are scary...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:42.500",
        "end": "01:43.500",
        "original": "そんなこと...",
        "english": "That's not...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:43.700",
        "end": "01:45.300",
        "original": "わかってるの。",
        "english": "I know it.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:45.400",
        "end": "01:47.500",
        "original": "おかしいよね、あんなのが、",
        "english": "It's weird, isn't it? To be...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:48.000",
        "end": "01:50.800",
        "original": "こんな、どうしようもなく怖いなんて。",
        "english": "...this helplessly terrified of them.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:52.000",
        "end": "01:57.000",
        "original": "だから、今日も我慢して、頑張ろうって、思ったのに。",
        "english": "That's why I thought I'd just endure it and do my best today.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:57.500",
        "end": "02:01.500",
        "original": "でも... でもやっぱり！",
        "english": "But... But I just can't!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:02.300",
        "end": "02:04.500",
        "original": "おかしくなんてないよ。",
        "english": "It's not weird at all.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:05.800",
        "end": "02:07.000",
        "original": "カノンさん...",
        "english": "Kanon-san...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:07.800",
        "end": "02:11.000",
        "original": "誰にだって、苦手なものがある。",
        "english": "Everyone has something they're not good at.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:11.100",
        "end": "02:13.000",
        "original": "怖いもの。嫌いなもの。",
        "english": "Things they fear. Things they hate.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:14.000",
        "end": "02:18.000",
        "original": "人に何でそんなものが、って言われても、",
        "english": "Even if people ask why you're bothered by such things,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:19.000",
        "end": "02:22.500",
        "original": "どうしようもないことって、やっぱりあるよ。",
        "english": "there are just some things you can't help.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:27.100",
        "end": "02:28.500",
        "original": "そうだよ！",
        "english": "That's right!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:28.600",
        "end": "02:32.500",
        "original": "何が苦手とか、何が怖いかとかは関係なくて、",
        "english": "What you're bad at or what you fear doesn't matter.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:32.600",
        "end": "02:37.000",
        "original": "大事なのは、今、ミオちゃんが辛いって思ってるかどうかだから！",
        "english": "What matters is whether you're hurting right now, Mio-chan!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:38.200",
        "end": "02:40.000",
        "original": "遠慮しないで。",
        "english": "Don't hold back.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:40.100",
        "end": "02:44.000",
        "original": "頼ってほしいにぇ！",
        "english": "I want you to lean on us!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:44.800",
        "end": "02:47.000",
        "original": "だって、そういうのさ。",
        "english": "Because, you know,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:47.100",
        "end": "02:51.000",
        "original": "うちら、お互い様じゃん！",
        "english": "we're all in this together!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:51.900",
        "end": "02:56.500",
        "original": "誰かの辛さ、誰かの苦手は、他の誰かがカバーする。",
        "english": "When one of us hurts or struggles, the others cover for them.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:56.600",
        "end": "03:00.000",
        "original": "お互い、そうやって、やってきたんだから！",
        "english": "That's how we've always made it through!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:00.000",
        "end": "03:01.500",
        "original": "今だって！",
        "english": "Even now!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:05.500",
        "end": "03:07.500",
        "original": "こんなに頑張れる！",
        "english": "We can fight this hard!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:10.800",
        "end": "03:14.000",
        "original": "ホロウィッチ、コラプターは、",
        "english": "holoWitches, the Corruptors",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:14.100",
        "end": "03:18.000",
        "original": "夢落ちした人の恐れと不安から生まれ、",
        "english": "are born from the fear and anxiety of the fallen,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:18.100",
        "end": "03:21.000",
        "original": "その心を深く沈ませてしまう。",
        "english": "sinking their hearts into the depths.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:21.800",
        "end": "03:24.500",
        "original": "夢落ちって、どうしてそれを...？",
        "english": "The fallen? How do you know about that...?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:25.100",
        "end": "03:28.000",
        "original": "でも、私は知ってる。",
        "english": "But I know this.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:29.000",
        "end": "03:31.500",
        "original": "君たちなら、ホロウィッチなら、",
        "english": "If it's you, if it's the holoWitches,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:31.600",
        "end": "03:35.500",
        "original": "辛い、苦しい、悲しい、きつい...",
        "english": "no matter how painful, agonizing, or sad it gets...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:36.000",
        "end": "03:43.000",
        "original": "そんな、自分一人の力じゃ抜け出せない暗闇の中にいても、",
        "english": "even in a darkness you can't escape alone,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:45.000",
        "end": "03:48.500",
        "original": "夢を、光を届けてくれる。",
        "english": "you will bring forth dreams and light.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:50.000",
        "end": "03:51.500",
        "original": "任せて！",
        "english": "Leave it to us!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:57.600",
        "end": "04:00.000",
        "original": "さあ、みんな。ホロウィッチが戦ってくれる。",
        "english": "Now, everyone. The holoWitches are fighting for us.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:02.500",
        "end": "04:05.500",
        "original": "では、私たちにできるのは？",
        "english": "So, what can we do?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:06.500",
        "end": "04:09.000",
        "original": "そう、私たちの声で、思いで、",
        "english": "That's right, with our voices and our feelings,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:11.000",
        "end": "04:14.500",
        "original": "彼女たちを応援することだ！",
        "english": "we must cheer them on!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:16.000",
        "end": "04:19.500",
        "original": "いざ、トリック・オア・トリート！",
        "english": "Now, Trick or Treat!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:22.500",
        "end": "04:24.500",
        "original": "仮装狂騒曲",
        "english": "Masquerade Rhapsody",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:24.500",
        "end": "04:26.000",
        "original": "作詞：TOPHAMHAT-KYO (FAKE TYPE.)",
        "english": "Lyrics: TOPHAMHAT-KYO (FAKE TYPE.)",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:26.000",
        "end": "04:27.500",
        "original": "作曲：FAKE TYPE.",
        "english": "Composition: FAKE TYPE.",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:28.100",
        "end": "04:30.800",
        "original": "あれよという間に飲み込まれ",
        "english": "Swallowed up in the blink of an eye",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:31.000",
        "end": "04:34.500",
        "original": "橙色のタイダルウェーブ やっこ やっこ",
        "english": "An orange tidal wave, heave-ho, heave-ho",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:34.900",
        "end": "04:37.900",
        "original": "ハンドメイドからオーダーメイドまで仕掛ける大流行",
        "english": "From handmade to custom-made, starting a huge craze",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:38.100",
        "end": "04:41.100",
        "original": "蜘蛛の巣から見せ物小屋まで纏めて大集合",
        "english": "From spider webs to sideshow tents, everyone gather 'round",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:41.300",
        "end": "04:44.200",
        "original": "添えも添えたり不遇な世界に お揃いの装束で ヘケケケケ",
        "english": "Adding more to this unfortunate world in matching outfits, hee-hee-hee-hee",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:44.300",
        "end": "04:47.500",
        "original": "これ見よがしの奴隷よ どおしようどれい？ 呪術的フォーメーションで ホップ ステップ トレイン",
        "english": "Look at these slaves, what to do, slaves? In a magical formation, hop step train",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:47.800",
        "end": "04:49.100",
        "original": "メーデーが特急から",
        "english": "Mayday from the express train",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:49.200",
        "end": "04:50.600",
        "original": "ジョニーをどつければ",
        "english": "If we wallop Johnny",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:50.700",
        "end": "04:53.900",
        "original": "チヤホヤしたりされたりがいいでしょ？ 今更じゃ物足りない義務感も",
        "english": "Pampering and being pampered feels good, right? Obligation isn't enough anymore",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:54.000",
        "end": "04:59.800",
        "original": "茶劇は一旦切って エブリバディ ご機嫌 エブリタイム センシティブ ティブ チグハグ お祭り騒ぎの 始まりだ",
